## BOUNDARY (Edge Conditions)

```
⊖ dead_hand_control       .60 | tyranny of the past self; mitigation via C4
⊖ ratified_coercion       .55 | began under duress, later freely reaffirmed; passes C1 via delay
⊖ self_deception          .50 | binds but based on false self-model; falls to C3 audit
⊖ irreversible_harm_oath  .65 | checked by C5 (Recursive Subordination)
```
